layout.text: KIM KARDASHIAN EXPLAINS WHY HER DAUGHTER NORTH HELD UP A STOP SIGN AT PARIS FASHION WEEK

On Wednesday, Kim Kardashian's daughter North asked photographers to stop taking pictures of her during the Jean-Paul Gaultier Haute Couture Fall/Winter 2022/2023 fashion show. The 9-year-old girl, who matched her mom with glasses and nose rings, held the sign up with a serious face in the clip to be found in Kim Kardashian's publication.
